Fetch and checkout the existing branch specified below.

<repository>{{ repository_url }}</repository>

<branch>{{ ref }}</branch>

Follow these exact steps:
<step number="1">
  Use the `run_git_command` tool to fetch the branch:
  <git_command>
    git fetch origin {{ ref }}
